{"tid":811172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿里巴巴：馬雲周一宣布繼任計劃, 過渡期間繼續擔任主席","createTime":"2018-09-08T14:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T02:15:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6437a5b39ca5402d777962626c57985371a40e","tid":811172,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://invest.hket.com/article/2156922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2156922&d=X6rhx2bzFlrsuPJ%2BUbrbMk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=367d81b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://invest.hket.com/article/2156922</a><br />\n<br />\n阿里：馬雲周一宣布繼任計劃 退休說法有誤<br />\n即時財經22:12 2018/09/08<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴（美：BABA）旗下《南華早報》報道，阿里巴巴董事局主席馬雲將會在周一（10日）54歲生日時宣布繼任計劃，為集團較年輕的管理層舖路接班。在過度期間，馬雲會繼續擔任集團的執行主席，而非外界所指的退任或退休。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》引述阿里巴巴發言人指，外媒報道馬雲「退休（retire）」的說法有誤，並非馬雲的本意。《紐約時報》較早前報道，馬雲會在周一辭去董事局主席職務，但會擔任董事，花更多精力在教育方面。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲在2013年將行政總裁職務交棒予張勇，並開始淡出集團的日常管理運作及專注公益，包括成立馬雲公益基金會。"},{"pid":"5c0f26809b3b98686304db44b166e37edf95e88d","tid":811172,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5a9a950b1c84d741e8000849881374077a01f6","tid":811172,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"想退莊保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd4c8ee85d2abdd5ee75b8294503693c27b3725","tid":811172,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff5a9a950b1c84d741e8000849881374077a01f6","tid":811172,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"想退莊保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實正常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3224f237150fca50924f2a7f54502